movie_name: A Vítima Invisível: O Caso Eliza Samudio
short_description: The disappearance of Eliza Samudio and her four-month-old son made headlines in Brazil. The main suspect was the child's father. Eight people were convicted for the kidnapping and murder of Eliza, but her body was never found.
